quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,"GooŇč…óii malaama gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  23,2,"∆Āeen huloo…ďe ka ndeer Juulde ma…ď…ďe ko…ďe yankinii…ďe."
  23,3,"E …ďeen …óurnii…ďe ga rayrayti( bolle mehre)."
  23,4,"E …ďeen ittoo…ďe askal on."
  23,5,"E …ďeen reen…ďe farjuuji ma…ď…ďe …ói."
  23,6,"Si wonaa e dow suddii…ďe ma…ď…ďe ma …ďe √Īaame ma…ď…ďe …óe njeyi(horbe), haray kam…ďe …ďe ngonaa feletee…ďe."
  23,7,"OOn mo …óa…ď…ďi …ďaawo …óum, haray ko …ďeen ngoni jaggitoo…ďe …ďen."
  23,8,"E …ďeen aynu…ďe koolaaje ma…ď…ďe e aadiiji ma…ď…ďe …ói."
  23,9,"E …ďeen …ďe ka√Īun ko…ďe reen…ďe e dow Juulde ma…ď…ďe …óen."
  23,10,"∆Āee [sifor…ďe …óii sifaaji …óoo] ko kam…ďe ngoni ronoo…ďe …ďen."
  23,11,"∆Āeen ronoyat…ďe Firdawsi on kam…ďe ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe e ndeer makko."
  23,12,"GooŇč…óii Min tagii ne…ó…óaŇčke on immorde e lasili loopal."
  23,13,"Refti Min mba…ói mo to…ď…ďere [maniiyu] e ndeer √Īii…ďirde ku…ďindiinde."
  23,14,"Refti Min Tagi to…ď…ďere nde he…ó…óere, Min Tagi he…ó…óere nden huyre, Min Tagi huyre nde ∆īi'e, Min koltini ∆īi'e …óeteewu. Refti Min pu…ó…óanii mo Tagoore woo, barkanii Alla Mo∆ī∆īo Tak…óo."
  23,15,"Refti onon …ďaawo …óuum ko on maayoo…ďe."
  23,16,"Refti pellet, onon √Ďande Darngal on imminoyte."
  23,17,"GooŇč…óii Min Tagii dow moo…óon …óati jee…ói…ói, Min ngonaani kadi welsindii…ďe gaayi tagoore nde."